data.description: Pinehurst living at its best. One story all brick home on a large private lot.  Home has been totally painted and ready for new owner. All living areas are beautiful hardwoods. Floor plan features split bedroom which are all ensuite,  huge pantry or storage room off kitchen, laundry with sink.  Garage with golf cart storage. This is the perfect home for entertaining with spacious bedrooms and large deck.  Location is very near entrance and on a quiet cul de sac.  Do not miss your opportunity for the perfect home!
